decks.notes: This deck focuses on quick and aggressive plays to deal damage to the opponent as fast as possible. It includes a mix of burn spells and creatures with haste to apply pressure early in the game. The goal is to maintain a fast pace and overwhelm the opponent before they have a chance to set up their own strategy. It prioritizes efficiency and direct damage, utilizing cards like Lightning Bolt, Boros Charm, and Monastery Swiftspear to quickly reduce the opponent's life total and secure a victory.

This deck revolves around utilizing Jeskai Ascendancy to generate infinite mana and card draw while untapping creatures to win the game in a single turn. The deck runs a variety of color fixing cards, card draw spells, and mana dorks to set up the combo quickly. Glittering Wish allows for access to key combo pieces from the sideboard, while Fatestitcher and Birds of Paradise provide additional ways to generate mana. The goal is to assemble Jeskai Ascendancy, mana dorks, and card draw spells to create a powerful combo engine and overwhelm the opponent in a single explosive turn.
